data.text: Pitch for funds by @u_nebraska and @CityofBellevue to be used to build an $80 million national defense innovation hub, senators discussed if casinos should get TIF,  a vaccine mandate bill advanced despite opposition from both sides.

Between Friday through today, there are 3 new cases of COVID19 on the Winnebago Reservation in Nebraska:
1 unvaccinated
1 vaccinated 
1 had booster 
There are 4 active and 4 households in quarantine, 1 hospitalized, and 1 reinfection. Total is 765. 

71% vaccination rate for 5+.

#Gophers announced today that they will not extend their temporary proof of COVID-19 vaccination or proof of a negative tests for fans to attend home games after Wednesday. And U men's and women's hoops teams are on the road tomorrow at Nebraska and Iowa. @StribSports
